title: Tricky Business
resume: Tricky Business is an Australian television drama series first broadcast on the Nine Network on 14 May 2012. Filmed in and around Wollongong and Sydney, the program is produced by Screentime with the assistance of Screen Australia. The Nine Network has ordered 13 episodes, with more to be determined by audience reception.The series premiered in New Zealand on 4 September 2012 on TV3.
